Class GameUnit

java.lang.Object
GameUnit
Direct Known Subclasses:
Dot, Ghost, Player, Wall
public abstract class GameUnit extends Object
GameUnit Class Implement basic game unit behaviours, Especially the direction, coordinates, collision box, original position, game manager that can manipulate this unit (in fact, it is mutually exclusive for each unit, if there is 1, there is no 0, and vice versa)
